720925f-b.text:
Laxington Avenue, west side, north from East 24th Street. View No. 2 is limited to tho blockfront extending to 25th Street. The three larger buildings in the midground are, an office structure at the S. W. corner of East 26th Street, the 69th Negiment Armory and the American Book Co. Building. The latter is at the N. W. corner of East 27th Street. In the background, at 42nd Street, appears the
towering Chanin and Chrysler Buildings.
No. 1: February 22, 1931
2: February 4, 1928
P. L. Sperr
